Relationship	Wrap object	Replace algorithm
🧾 1️⃣4️⃣ Final Interview Summary

Decorator Pattern allows adding new behavior to an object dynamically by wrapping it, avoiding subclass explosion and promoting flexible design.

🔑 1️⃣5️⃣ Memory Trick
Decorator → “Wrap and add features”
